title: Tom Petty - Leave Virginia Alone (Official Music Video)
description:
Official Music Video for Tom Petty's "Leave Virginia Alone' from 'Wildflowers & All The Rest' 

The album, Wildflowers, released in 1994, is commonly vaunted as Tom Petty‚Äôs most personal, most heartfelt, and most revealing artistic statement of his career. Recorded over the course of two years and originally intended to be a two-disc album, it was perhaps the most creative period in his life.

The release of Wildflowers & All The Rest on Oct 16, 2020 will finally gather together all 25 songs from the original recording sessions ‚Äì the 15 songs from Wildflowers, plus the 10 songs that were left off the original release.
